      KrisFlyer is proud to be the Official Lifestyle Rewards Partner of th=
e <strong>OneRepublic "From Asia, With Love" 2026 in Singapore</strong> con=
cert, which will be held on 2 March 2026 at the Singapore Indoor Stadium. K=
risFlyer members can enjoy exclusive priority access to secure tickets to t=
his electrifying performance. <br><br>
    During the KrisFlyer Presale from <strong>18 November 2025, 12:00hr (GM=
T+8) to 19 November 2025, 12:00hr (GMT+8)</strong>, members can choose betw=
een purchasing tickets on Ticketmaster, or redeeming tickets with miles via=
 the <a href=3D"https://t.email.singaporeair.com/r/=3Fid=3Dh7b71af9b,6cc2af=
