     Members who wish to purchase tickets on Ticketmaster during the KrisFl=
yer Presale must register their interest <a href=3D"https://t.email.singapo=
reair.com/r/=3Fid=3Dh7b71af9b,6cc2af4b,38586d19" target=3D"_blank"><font>he=
re</font></a> and subscribe to receive KrisFlyer and Singapore Airlines Gro=
up Promotions email communication in their KrisFlyer profile <strong>by 13 =
November 2025, 10:59hr (GMT+8)</strong>, to receive a private link and acce=
ss code. Only one access code will be sent per KrisFlyer account. This acce=
ss code will be <strong>sent to eligible members by 16 November 2025, 23:59=
hr (GMT+8)</strong> and payment of the tickets must be paid for with a Mast=
ercard<sup style=3D" font-size:9px; line-height: 0;">&reg;</sup> credit or =
debit card. <br><br>
   You do not need to register for the KrisFlyer Presale if you are redeemi=
ng miles for the ticket(s).<br><br>
     With KrisFlyer, experiences are miles better.
